               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Homily by Rǝtuʿa Hāymānot on the Four Living Creatures (fols.
                     5ra-14ra)
 II) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael
                     (fols. 15ra-26rb)
 II-1) Homily by an anonymous author for the 12th of
                     Ḫǝdār [Tāḫśāś] (fols. 15ra-19vb)
 II-2) Homily by Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of
                     ʾAksum [for Sane] (fols. 19vb-26rb)
 III)Taʾammǝra Mikāʾel "Miracles of
                     Michael": 4 miracles (fols. 26rb-31ra)
 IV) Nǝgǝränni sǝmäkä ... "Tell me
                     your name ..." (fols. 31ra-32rb)</summary>
