               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origPlace>
                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0123MKL">Laqāy Kidāna Mǝḥrat</placeName>
                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1700" notAfter="1750">The Ms. was written by <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12076ZawaldaMaryam">Zawalda Māryām</persName> who
                        was active in the first half of the 18th cent. (s. the colophon of Ms.
                        QSM-007, <locus target="#217rb">217rb</locus>.)</origDate>
                  </origin>
               <provenance>The original donor was probably Diyonasyos
                     whose name is mentioned throughout the Ms. He is stated as the commissioner of
                     the miniature on 14vb. 
 The names of Gabra
                     Krǝstos, ʿAmda Mikāʾel, Fäsilädas and Gabra Śǝllāse are written in a secondary
                     hand (brown ink) on 14rab and were added to the
                     supplication formulas throughout the Ms.</provenance></history>
